  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view captures a cityscape bathed in the vibrant hues of a sunset or sunrise. The sky is ablaze with a gradient of colors, transitioning from deep reds and oranges near the horizon to a lighter, almost pastel shade higher up. Silhouetted against this dramatic sky are the outlines of buildings and infrastructure, including a prominent bridge with illuminated lights stretching across the water. The water itself appears a deep, almost indigo blue, reflecting the colors of the sky and dotted with twinkling lights. The scene evokes a sense of tranquility and grandeur.",
